name: Circular Gallifreyan Tumblr Logo
description: Replaces the Tumblr logo with Tumblr written in Circular Gallifreyan
additional_info: Created using this guide (http://timeturners.wikidot.com/circular-gallifreyan), this logo replaces the tumblr words usually seen on the dashboard with Tumblr written in the language of the Doctor's home planet, Gallifrey. A must-have for every Whovian!
